<h1><i class="fa fa-users"></i>Users</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><i class="fa fa-users"></i>Users</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= application.name %> can be used by a wide variety of people for a wide variety of uses.  The platform can be used by individuals or by various type of groups, large or small. </p>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-user"></i>Individuals</h2>
				<p>Although <%= application.name %> was designed to help groups of people collaborate, it also works great to help you as an individual user.  <%= application.name %> can be used to back up your files, to share files with your associates, and even to share files between your devices (mobile, tablet, or desktop). </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img class="attention" src="images/info/users/person.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-users"></i>Special Interest Groups</h2>
				<p>If you are part of a club or a group of people who share a particular interest, <%= application.name %> can help you to connect and share. You can make the platform that you use to communicate reflect your own particular interests and values. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="icons figure">
					<img src="images/info/users/sigs/1f9b8-1f3fb-200d-2642-fe0f.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/sigs/1f9d1-1f3fb-200d-1f3a8.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/sigs/1f9d1-1f3fb-200d-1f680.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/sigs/1f9d1-1f3fe-200d-1f33e.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/sigs/1f9d9-1f3fb-200d-2642-fe0f.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/sigs/1f9da-1f3fb-200d-2640-fe0f.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-dna"></i>Families</h2>
				<p>You can use <%= application.name %>to set up a website specifically for your family and relatives. You don't need to rely upon Big Social just to communicate amongst yourselves.  By setting up your own platform, you can opt out of censorship, surveillance, and advertising. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="small icons figure">
					<img src="images/info/users/family/1F466.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/family/1F467.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/family/1F468.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/family/1F469.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/family/1F474.svg" />
					<img src="images/info/users/family/1F475.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-briefcase"></i>Small Businesses</h2>
				<p>If you run a small business, <%= application.name %> is a great way to share files and messages among your colleagues or with external clients.  For internal use, you can configure the platform to meet your company's needs.  For external use, the platform can be customized to match your company branding and identity so you will stand out to your clients. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/users/computer.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-microscope"></i>Laboratories</h2>
				<p>If you run either a laboratory, whether it's commercial, academic, or government bases, <%= application.name %> can help you to share data among your fellow researchers. <%= application.name %> can be used to view various types of scientific data and the sharing features make it a snap to share very large directories of data. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/users/microscope.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-blackboard"></i>Classrooms</h2>
				<p><%= application.name %> can be used by schools and classrooms to allow teachers and classmates to share information safely and securely.  By hosting and controlling your own platform, you can provide students with a secure environment that's also easy to use. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/users/teacher.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-institution"></i>University Departments</h2>
				<p>If you run a university department, regulations often require that communications be recorded in case of FOIA requests.  If you use commercial providers, this usually requires a paid subscription.  By managing your own data, you control it and can retain it as long as you want. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/users/university.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-user-secret"></i>Sensitive Data Users</h2>
				<p>If you work with sensitive data, then it's likely that you can't use internet based commercial providers.  You may even run on a SCIF (Sensitive Compartmented Information Facility) or an internal network.  In these cases, you will need a self-hosted solution that can be deployed and controlled on your secure network. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img src="images/info/users/spy.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-landmark-dome"></i>Government Agencies</h2>
				<p>Government agencies are beginning to look for alternatives to commercial cloud providers in order to regain soverignty and control over public data. Public data should not be held hostage to corporate control. <%= application.name %> can help us to move towards a more equitable model for our citizens. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<img class="attention" src="images/info/users/capitol.svg" />
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>